================================================================================
EXTERNAL DATA AND DATABASE LICENSES
================================================================================

This repository integrates data from public databases with their own licenses:

1. Open Targets Platform v24.12
   - License: CC-BY 4.0
   - URL: https://platform.opentargets.org/
   - Citation: Carvalho-Silva et al. 2023, Nucleic Acids Research

2. Ensembl VEP
   - License: Apache 2.0 (software) + EMBL-EBI (data)
   - URL: https://www.ensembl.org/Tools/VEP
   - Citation: McLaren et al. 2016, Genome Biology

3. RNAct Database
   - License: Open access
   - URL: https://rnact.crg.eu/

4. ChEMBL
   - License: CC-BY 4.0
   - URL: https://www.ebi.ac.uk/chembl/
   - Citation: Mendez et al., Nucleic Acids Research

5. GTEx Portal
   - License: CC-BY 4.0
   - URL: https://gtexportal.org/

6. ToppGene Suite
   - License: Free for academic use
   - URL: https://toppgene.cchmc.org/
   - Citation: Chen et al. 2009, Bioinformatics

Users must respect the licenses of these external databases when using derived data.

